OL,5, US Defence Secretary Lloyd Austin has  
OL,6, been pressed by lawmakers for not      
OL,7, informing the White House of recent    
OL,8, hospital stays, with one calling the   
OL,9, failure an "embarrassment".            
OL,11,FThe Pentagon chief acknowledged there  
OL,12,Fwas "a breakdown in notifications"     
OL,13,Fabout his January hospital stay during 
OL,14,Fa contentious Thursday hearing.        
OL,16,FMr Austin, 70, has been undergoing     
OL,17,Fprostate cancer treatment.             
OL,19,FThe Pentagon has found no "indication  
OL,20,Fof ill intent" by Mr Austin.           
